{
  "texts": [
    "Fisher's exact test supported these results (p = 0.013).",
    "The reported effect size was moderate, however, indicating a moderate association between the two variables, Cramer's V = 0.229.",
    "The confusion matrix is shown in Table 16.",
    "These results suggest that automatic AI detection systems mainly tended to attribute the stimuli to human authors.",
    "However, none of the stimuli obfuscated by Undetectable.AI were detected as being generated by an AI, whereas the automatic AI detection systems attributed a small percentage of ChatGPT-generated texts to AI."
  ]
}